      <div class="disclose__body">
        <p><strong>This is an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not QuickBooks&rsquo; official support.</strong> If your problem is really an Intuit account, login, password, subscription, or billing issue, Intuit&rsquo;s own support is the right path: <a href="https://quickbooks.intuit.com/learn-support/" rel="noopener nofollow">Intuit support &rarr;</a>. What we do is the operational accounting work inside your own books &mdash; setting QuickBooks up, cleaning it up, migrating it, and running it. Our ProAdvisor certification is verifiable in Intuit&rsquo;s public directory. QuickBooks and Intuit are registered trademarks of Intuit Inc.</p>
